---
import MainLayout from "../layout/mainLayout.astro";
import LineBreaker from "../components/lineBreaker.astro";
import SectionLayout from "../layout/sectionLayout.astro";
import Carousel from "../components/carousel.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>Home</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <MainLayout>
      <Carousel folderUrl="/home/carousel" itemsCount={5} />
      <SectionLayout containerClass="flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="font-bold text-2xl text-center">Our Goals</div>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-10 flex-wrap">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 items-center w-[min(300px,100%)]">
            <img src="/home/goals1.webp" alt="" class="max-h-[150px]" />
            <div class="font-semibold text-base text-center">
              Local Economic Development
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm w-[70%] text-center">
              We focus on supporting local economies by providing jobs, goods,
              and services within the community contributing to the overall
              economic development and resilience of the area.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 items-center w-[min(300px,100%)]">
            <img src="/home/goals2.webp" alt="" class="max-h-[150px]" />
            <div class="font-semibold text-base text-center">
              Social Responsibility
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm w-[70%] text-center">
              One of our primary goals is to meet the needs of their members and
              communities, promoting sustainability and ethical business
              practices.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 items-center w-[min(300px,100%)]">
            <img src="/home/goals3.webp" alt="" class="max-h-[150px]" />
            <div class="font-semibold text-base text-center">
              Mutual Support and Solidarity
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm w-[70%] text-center">
              Our members work together for mutual benefit fostering a sense of
              community and solidarity, where they support each other
              economically and socially.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </SectionLayout>
      <LineBreaker />
      <SectionLayout
        containerClass="flex justify-center gap-6 max-[900px]:flex-wrap max-[900px]:justify-center"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <div class="font-bold text-2xl">Founder&apos;s Vision</div>
          <span class="text-sm max-w-[600px] text-justify">
            At the inception of The New India Multipurpose Co-operative Society
            - NIMS, our founder envisioned a transformative journey towards a
            sustainable and healthier future for India. Embracing the principles
            of cooperation and multipurpose engagement, NIMS was established
            with the vision to create a dynamic and inclusive platform that
            serves as a catalyst for the organic movement in the country. Our
            founder's dream is to foster a community where the cultivation and
            consumption of organic products become synonymous with a vibrant,
            eco-conscious lifestyle. NIMS aims to be the epicenter of this
            positive change, promoting not only organic farming but also
            providing a multifaceted cooperative society that empowers
            individuals, uplifts communities, and contributes to the holistic
            development of our nation. Through innovation, collaboration, and a
            commitment to ethical practices, NIMS aspires to be the driving
            force behind a New India that thrives on health, sustainability, and
            shared prosperity.
          </span>
        </div>
        <img src="/home/founderVision.webp" alt="" class="max-h-[300px]" />
      </SectionLayout>
      <LineBreaker />
      <SectionLayout containerClass="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="font-bold text-[1.5rem]">Products and Services</div>
        <div class="text-sm max-w-[700px]">
          Harvesting sustainability, our cooperative thrives on cultivating
          organic goodness. From farm-fresh fruits to eco-friendly biogas
          systems, we're rooted in a community that grows together. Nourishing
          both body and planet, we empower members with financial services,
          fostering a sustainable future where every seed planted yields
          abundance for all.
        </div>
        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-[repeat(2,400px)] gap-2 overflow-hidden mt-6 grid-rows-[repeat(3,160px)] truncate max-[900px]:grid-cols-[min(400px,100%)] justify-center"
        >
          <a
            href="/organic-store/vegetables"
            class="relative row-span-1 truncate rounded-md [&:hover>img]:scale-110"
          >
            <img
              src="/home/products1.webp"
              alt=""
              class="h-full w-full object-cover transition duration-200"
            />
            <div
              class="bg-[#F9C22F] p-2 absolute bottom-0 left-0 rounded-md text-white font-semibold"
            >
              Organic Fruits and Vegetables
            </div>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/biogas"
            class="relative row-span-2 truncate rounded-md [&:hover>img]:scale-110"
          >
            <img
              src="/home/products2.webp"
              alt=""
              class="h-full w-full object-cover transition duration-200"
            />
            <div
              class="bg-[#ED7225] p-2 absolute bottom-0 left-0 rounded-md text-white font-semibold"
            >
              Home Biogas Systems
            </div>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/organic-store/products"
            class="relative row-span-2 truncate rounded-md [&:hover>img]:scale-110"
          >
            <img
              src="/home/products3.webp"
              alt=""
              class="h-full w-full object-cover transition duration-200"
            />
            <div
              class="bg-[#89C832] p-2 absolute bottom-0 left-0 rounded-md text-white font-semibold"
            >
              Organic Products
            </div>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/mushrooms"
            class="relative row-span-1 truncate rounded-md [&:hover>img]:scale-110"
          >
            <img
              src="/home/products4.webp"
              alt=""
              class="h-full w-full object-cover transition duration-200"
            />
            <div
              class="bg-[#450F0A] p-2 absolute bottom-0 left-0 rounded-md text-white font-semibold"
            >
              Mushrooms
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </SectionLayout>
      <LineBreaker />
      <SectionLayout containerClass="flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="font-bold text-[1.5rem] text-center">News/Awards</div>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 flex-wrap">
          <div
            class="p-2 drop-shadow-[0px_0px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] rounded w-[250px] bg-white"
          >
            <img src="/home/article1.webp" alt="" />
            <div class="font-semibold text-sm text-center">
              NIMS Featured in Latest NavHind Times newspaper yet again
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="p-2 drop-shadow-[0px_0px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] rounded w-[250px] bg-white"
          >
            <img src="/home/article1.webp" alt="" />
            <div class="font-semibold text-sm text-center">
              NIMS Featured in Latest NavHind Times newspaper yet again
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="p-2 drop-shadow-[0px_0px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] rounded w-[250px] bg-white"
          >
            <img src="/home/article1.webp" alt="" />
            <div class="font-semibold text-sm text-center">
              NIMS Featured in Latest NavHind Times newspaper yet again
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </SectionLayout>
    </MainLayout>
  </body>
</html>
